title: IAlarmStateChangedListener2 (Interface)
text:
INTERFACE IAlarmStateChangedListener2 EXTENDS
IAlarmStateChangedListener
This interface extends the interface IAlarmStateChangedListener to call its
method AlarmDeactivationStateChanged() in case the deactivation state of an alarm changed.
